  <description><![CDATA[<p>Get ready for coastal drives and journeys through the unspoiled landscapes of <a data-udi="umb://document/c7d9c305cd1e44568dec1178157bc9f9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c7d9c305cd1e44568dec1178157bc9f9}" title="Sardinia">Sardinia</a>. Why see just one area of this beautiful island when there's so much to explore. We've planned an itinerary that means you can see the best bits without having to worry about organising a thing - just jump in the car and hit the road. Cruise along the spectacular eastern coast, beside the Orosei Gulf, taking in the clear blue waters. Spend days exploring prehistoric villages like Serra Orrios and visit the castle acropolis at Cagliari. </p>
<p>Other highlights on your journey through millennial olive groves and Mediterranean landscapes include visiting the UNESCO protected megalithic villages of Barumini, wandering the cobbled palazzi lined streets of Alghero’s centro sotico and hopping between the islands of La Maddalena Archipelago.</p>
<p><span>This holiday is also available starting from Cagliari airport, please call to book.</span></p>
